segment.source: The Windows Performance Toolkit (WPT) consists of performance tools that produce in-depth performance profiles of Windows operating systems and applications.
segment.target: The Windows Performance Toolkit (WPT) consists of performance tools that produce in-depth performance profiles of Windows operating systems and applications.

segment.source: The Windows Assessment Toolkit (WAT) contains assessments that help you determine the performance, reliability, and functionality of a running operating system or a set of components.
segment.target: The Windows Assessment Toolkit (WAT) contains assessments that help you determine the performance, reliability, and functionality of a running operating system or a set of components.
